These be the articles folovvynge the vvhiche the kynges grace hathe pardoned Proclamations. 1509-04-24 England and Wales. Sovereign (1509-1547 : Henry VIII)
1 sheet ([1] p.)
R. Faques, [London : 1509]
Henry VIII's accession pardon: a list of the crimes pardoned if committed before 24 April 1509. Imprint from STC; Steele suggests R. Pynson as printer. The first four words of the title are xlyographic, white on black. In this edition, line 3 of text: prouffytes. Imperfect; torn, affecting text. Reproduction of the original in the Cambridge University Library.
